                    <h3 class="session-title">use Embassy; Impl Snake for Micro:bit</h3>
                    <span class="session-time">04:30 - 05:00</span>
                    <span class="session-presenter">Cyril MARPAUD</span>
                </div>

                <div class="session session-1 track-3" style="grid-column: track-3; grid-row: time-0430 / time-0500;">
                    <h3 class="session-title">Superpowers of Angular Directives</h3>
                    <span class="session-time">04:30 - 05:0</span>
                    <span class="session-presenter">Armen Vardanyan</span>
                </div>

                <div class="session session-1 track-4" style="grid-column: track-4; grid-row: time-0430 / time-0500;">
                    <h3 class="session-title">Build conversational AI experiences powered by LLMs</h3>
                    <span class="session-time">04:30 - 05:00</span>
                    <span class="session-presenter">Xavier Portilla Edo</span>
                </div>

                <div class="session session-2 track-1" style="grid-column: track-1; grid-row: time-0500 / time-0530;">
                    <h3 class="session-title">Migrating your conventional Angular Workspace to a Monorepo in a busy company</h3>
                    <span class="session-time">05:00 - 05:30</span>
                    <span class="session-presenter">Anirudh Varma</span>
                </div>

                <div class="session session-2 track-2" style="grid-column: track-2; grid-row: time-0500 / time-0530;">
                    <h3 class="session-title">Lessons Learned from Building a Serverless Notifications System</h3>
                    <span class="session-time">05:00 - 05:30</span>
                    <span class="session-presenter">Srushith Repakula</span>
                </div>

                <div class="session session-2 track-3" style="grid-column: track-3; grid-row: time-0500 / time-0530;">
                    <h3 class="session-title">Writing for Software Engineers</h3>
                    <span class="session-time">05:00 - 05:30</span>
                    <span class="session-presenter">Ankur Tyagi</span>
