                    <h3 class="session-title">Angular 17 Unveiled: Revolutionizing Developer Experience</h3>
                    <span class="session-time">06:00 - 06:30</span>
                    <span class="session-presenter">Deepa Chaurasia</span>
                </div>

                <div class="session session-4 track-2" style="grid-column: track-2; grid-row: time-0600 / time-0630;">
                    <h3 class="session-title">Securing Your Django Applications: Best Practices</h3>
                    <span class="session-time">06:00 - 06:30</span>
                    <span class="session-presenter">Sophia Iroegbu</span>
                </div>

                <div class="session session-4 track-3" style="grid-column: track-3; grid-row: time-0600 / time-0630;">
                    <h3 class="session-title">Schema First Approach to Typescript Types Design</h3>
                    <span class="session-time">06:00 - 06:30</span>
                    <span class="session-presenter">Maina Wycliffe</span>
                </div>

                <div class="session session-4 track-4" style="grid-column: track-4; grid-row: time-0600 / time-0630;">
                    <h3 class="session-title">Advancing Generative AI integration with Vertex AI Node.js SDK</h3>
                    <span class="session-time">06:00 - 06:30</span>
                    <span class="session-presenter">Patty O'Callaghan</span>
                </div>

                <div class="session session-5 track-1" style="grid-column: track-1; grid-row: time-0630 / time-0700;">
                    <h3 class="session-title">A nerdy guide to the web trending concepts</h3>
                    <span class="session-time">06:30 - 07:00</span>
                    <span class="session-presenter">Daniel Afonso</span>
                </div>

                <div class="session session-5 track-2" style="grid-column: track-2; grid-row: time-0630 / time-0700;">
                    <h3 class="session-title">Meet Your New BFF: Backend to Frontend without the Duct Tape</h3>
