                    <span class="session-presenter">Noam Honig</span>
                </div>

                <div class="session session-5 track-3" style="grid-column: track-3; grid-row: time-0630 / time-0700;">
                    <h3 class="session-title">TypeScript's 'Never' Type: The Invisible Force Shaping Code?</h3>
                    <span class="session-time">06:30 - 07:00</span>
